More than 100 sailboats and as many as 200 people were participating in the Dauphin Island regatta in Mobile Bay, Alabama .
The storm rolled through the area about 4 p.m. and a man was plucked from the waters by the Coast Guard around 9 a.m., Petty officer Carlos Vega said .
'We knew we were totally lost at sea,' said the Buccaneer yacht club president .